{
  "texts": [
    "In our example, performance is measured using the balanced accuracy, and fairness is measured using the equalised odds difference.",
    "The grid search technique can provide the practitioner with a choice of models that suits their accuracy and fairness thresholds.",
    "In our example, all models trained are LightGBM with differing hyperparameters (i.e.",
    "the parameters controlling the depth, number of leaves, etc.",
    "of the LightGBM model)."
  ]
}